# Cloudflare Pages / Netlify rewrite rules.
# Serve the Go vanity import meta (public/mitos/index.html) with HTTP 200 for
# /mitos and every subpath, so `go get mitos.run/mitos/...` resolves at any
# import depth. Status 200 makes these rewrites, not redirects (go-get needs
# the meta in the final 200 response).
/mitos        /mitos/index.html   200
/mitos/*      /mitos/index.html   200
